{[#]} 1... cxd4 $1 {This is the right moment to release the central tension.
White is forced to recapture with the c-pawn and his knight is on d2.} 2. cxd4
Nce8 $1 {Once again, we see this typical idea of rerouting the knight to d6.}
3. Rac1 Nd6 {Although Black's position looks slightly passive, I don't see any
idea for White to breakthrough.} *

